            "title": "港股開跌163點  阿里挫逾6%  李寧升7.85%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數開跌163點或0.64%，報25337，恒生科技指數開趺8點或0.97%，報4948點 ; 恒生國企指數開跌71點或0.82%，報8624。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市現成交56.4億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988)季績遜預期，開跌6.44%，報123元，成交居首。第二季淨利按年跌67%至167.1億元人幣，市場預期為316億元。騰訊(00700)跌1.56%，報505元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中遠海控(01919)跌1.57%，報15.7元，盈利趺37.24%，末期息減57.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">李寧(02331)高開7.85%，報21.3元，去年純利跌2.6%，末期息23.36分，增12.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代(-3750)升3.18%，報664.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紫金(02899)挫2.02%，報34元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">友邦(01299)升2.3%，報84.7元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15765199-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e8%b7%8c163%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be6-%e6%9d%8e%e5%af%a7%e5%8d%877-85",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240420240415_FI_source-web_HKSTOCK.png.png.webp",
